09-09T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746f958f0e8a7070bb962b96ead180ff3a74a3d6","tid":1555141,"uid":9049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9a3d5642b512d629b8a17430d00779e4d9bca78d","tid":1555141,"uid":194690,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"二代好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"尊敬<br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n勇武走得太前，後勤補給不足，文宣唔夠人！<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，免費港鐵；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BunqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=cfe960e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 低消費，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.09"},{"pid":"00b602666a227f8d349d306ce809580d83a2c544","tid":1555141,"uid":30310,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"被個杯掟親都要瞓兩日醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53d8d1e98372e85d879737e141bba4be6398611","tid":1555141,"uid":49216,"like":0,"disli